rComments: Like I never thought I could pass this course but prof and TA saved me. He likes to give bonus maybe because we did really not good in term tests. The questions are too many in one midterm test and only less than one hour for it. Also, writing a term paper is so difficult and still need to give the presentation. But he is a very nice prof.

We were the first class he taught after his PHD so I don't blame him too much but his teaching style is really fast (he really needs to slow it down and explain each concept and give examples).... no one really gets what's going on in the course. His exams are fair but very long in the time given.
teacherRatingTags: ['Lots of homework', "Skip class? You won't pass.", 'Gives good feedback']
